'''高氏兄弟'''（{{Lang-en|Gao Brothers}}），中国当代艺术家组合，哥哥高兟生于1956年，弟弟高强生于1962年<ref>{{cite journal|title=高氏兄弟:生来不是为反抗|author=汪峥|journal=长城月报|issue=5|year=2011}}</ref>。二人均为[[山东省|山东]][[济南市|济南]]人，现居[[北京市|北京]]。1985年起合作，从事绘画、装置、行为等艺术活动。1989年的装置作品《子夜的弥撒》使二人一举成名<ref>{{cite book|author=吴虹飞|title=听我讲话要小心：文化名人访谈录|year=2011年|publisher=武汉出版社|isbn=9787543063402|pages=98-102|url=http://lz.book.sohu.com/chapter-1286656.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528031922/http://lz.book.sohu.com/chapter-1286656.html|archivedate=2015-05-28}}</ref>，并在90年代中期逐渐获得国际声誉<ref>{{cite web|title=The Gao Brothers: Old Haunts and New Visions|url=http://www.sfstation.com/the-gao-brothers-a5791|accessdate=2014-05-30|author=Gina Basso|publisher=SF Station {{!}} San Francisco's City Guide|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528031422/http://www.sfstation.com/the-gao-brothers-a5791|archivedate=2015-05-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2003年，二人在[[798艺术区|798艺术区]]开办工作室<ref name="wu">{{cite journal|title=高氏兄弟 被迫反抗的艺术|author=[[吴虹飞|吴虹飞]]|url=http://collection.sina.com.cn/cjrw/20101123/16342441.shtml|journal=南方人物周刊|accessdate=2014-05-30|issue=41|year=2010|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528001022/http://collection.sina.com.cn/cjrw/20101123/16342441.shtml|archivedate=2015-05-28|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

高氏兄弟不少作品触及中国政治，并表达他们对中国政治和社会的态度<ref>{{Cite web|title=Body politic: Gao Brothers photographs are naked criticism of modern|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/art/features/body-politic-gao-brothers-photographs-are-naked-criticism-modern-china-8658015.html|accessdate=2020-12-02|date=2013-06-14|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=高氏兄弟：用艺术为自由呐喊|url=http://helanonline.cn/article/4901|accessdate=2014-05-30|publisher=荷兰在线|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528001206/http://helanonline.cn/article/4901|archivedate=2015-05-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。这类作品一直引发巨大争议<ref>{{Cite web|title=专访：高氏兄弟谈中国荒诞现实与艺术|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/china/2013/06/130605_gao_brothers|accessdate=2020-12-02|date=2013-06-05|work=[[英国广播公司|BBC News 中文]]|language=zh-hans}}</ref>。有观者指责其表达过于直接，缺乏艺术性<ref>{{Cite news|title=In China, a Headless Mao Is a Game of Cat and Mouse (Published 2009)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/06/arts/design/06gao.html|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|date=2009-10-05|accessdate=2020-12-02|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jimmy|last=Wang}}</ref>，但亦有论者认为高氏兄弟的作品怀有「对正义，民主，诗意的热切情怀」<ref>{{cite web|title=当代性的充盈和嘹亮|url=http://www.artlinkart.com/cn/artist/txt_ge/d72auws/141cswpj|accessdate=2014-05-30|author=俞心樵|publisher=ARTLINKART {{!}} 中国当代艺术数据库|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528001528/http://www.artlinkart.com/cn/artist/txt_ge/d72auws/141cswpj|archivedate=2015-05-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

